# React & UI Rules

## Server vs Client

- `"use client"` only when needed (state, effects, events, router, charts)
- Portal layouts are client components wrapping `PortalShell`

## Page Skeleton

```tsx
<div className="space-y-6 p-4 md:p-8">
  <PageHeader title="..." description="..." action={...} />
  {/* content in rounded-2xl border bg-card cards */}
</div>
```

## Components

| Layer | Location | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| shadcn primitives | `components/ui/` | Do not modify for features |
| Shared | `components/shared/` | Reuse across portals |
| Feature | `components/customer|manager|washer/` | Domain logic here |

## Status & Tiers

Use `StatusBadge`, `TierBadge` from `@/components/status-badge` with types from `@/lib/types`.

## Toasts

Prefer `import { toast } from 'sonner'` in new manager/washer pages. Match neighboring files if editing existing pages.

## Forms

react-hook-form + zod + shadcn `Form` components. Show validation errors in Vietnamese.
